query_1_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U002' AND status = 'failed' AND timestamp <= '2025-06-26 18:38:10' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
query_2_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U002' AND timestamp BETWEEN '2025-06-26 00:00:00' AND '2025-06-26 23:59:59' AND location = 'Indonesia';
query_3_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.amount, t.timestamp, t.location, t.device_id, t.ip_address FROM transactions t JOIN alerts a ON t.transaction_id = a.transaction_id WHERE a.alert_id = '9a0ffcf7-1cde-468b-a47c-a18e7119d56e' AND t.user_id = 'U002';
query_4_sql: SELECT la.timestamp, la.ip_address, la.device_id FROM login_attempts la JOIN transactions t ON la.user_id = t.user_id WHERE t.transaction_id = 'd5c0244d-3735-462d-8184-3b0304dd7054' AND la.status = 'failed' ORDER BY la.timestamp DESC;
query_5_sql: SELECT d.device_id, d.device_type, d.os, d.last_seen_ip FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U002' AND d.last_seen_ip IN (SELECT ip_address FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U002' AND status = 'failed');
query_6_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as failed_count FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U002' AND status = 'failed' AND timestamp > datetime('now', '-24 hours')
query_8_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U002' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_9_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U002' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_11_sql: SELECT d.* FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U002';
